Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:13.75,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We will shine around the world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.75,0:01:16.55,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trip to the world{\i0}\N{\i1}Yo! Here we go unknown world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.59,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We newborn travelers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:20.79,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The unfamiliar walk is still charming{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:22.69,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The place you want to go is under your feet!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:24.03,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So many people in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:26.43,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not as if there isn't{\i0}\N{\i1}backstabbing once in a while{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:28.26,Style2,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's warp past these boring things{\i0}
